{
  "stem": "26585.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said, shh, your father is back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came that night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mother stripped him in the-- in the yard, in the courtyard totally, then lifted him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The man weighed approximately 156 pounds, normally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SOB] She picked him up like he was a doll and carried him upstairs, let water run in the tub, put him in the tub, washed him, gave him a bath, put warm pajamas, and put him in bed, and then ran downstairs and spooned soup.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he said he wants to see the girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now she put a robe on him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he came in the hallway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't recognize him, because they had shaved his head.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he-- his face looked like a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You've seen a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when he embraced us, it was-- you felt nothing but bones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SOB] I screamed so that Mother had to slap me and put me to bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then the next morning, I finally-- this-- this was one of the most horrible experiences of my life, because this was my father and it wasn't my father.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was so sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Our doctor came at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, he wasn't allowed to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was a very, very Catholic man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he said, Doctor, please, tell me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have a daughter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have to raise her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Please tell me what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my father said, I cannot tell you, because I was told if I opened my mouth to anybody, not only will I disappear, but my wife and my daughters will disappear.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I cannot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when-- I'm going ahead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we crossed the border from Germany into Yugoslavia, my mother said, Max, tell us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's when he told.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what he said, Liesel, what did you do?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
